About Us
Full Liquor
Bar & Grill
We specialize in a variety of mixed drinks & shots.
I
f you know it, we can make it!  If beer is more your style, we’ve got you covered there with domestics, crafts & ciders. Over 20 beers on tap.
We offer full kitchen service, dine in and carry out.  Serving you quality food, always fresh- never frozen.  We are known for our award winning chicken wings, with our homemade delicious  sauces.  Our hand pressed burgers will melt in your mouth and will surely have you wanting to come back to try them all.  They are so good, they earned us the honor of being voted into Tampa Bay’s Top 10 Burger List! If you are looking for as new favorite try our beef tenderloin steak bites!  They melt in your mouth and are bursting with flavor to die for!
